        "description": {
            "value": "<p>While looking straight down the barrel of this <em>+1 striking blunderbuss</em>, the spark gun's magical core is visible amid several reflectors. All damage dealt by a thundercrasher is sonic damage. On a critical hit, the target must succeed at a Fortitude save against your class DC or be @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Deafened] for 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> Interact</p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> You overload the <em>thundercrasher</em> to emit chaotic sonic frequencies that soften earth and stone. When you next fire the <em>thundercrasher</em> it also partially liquefies any natural earth or stone surfaces within range of its scatter trait, making the area difficult terrain.</p>"
